summary: It’s my birthday tommorow and for the past few years my mom has been printing out her own birthday cards for me instead of...
body:
It’s my birthday tommorow and for the past few years my mom has been printing out her own birthday cards for me instead of buying one and usually making them themed on something she knows I’m into at the time(for instance she gave me a Gravity Falls one a year or two ago etc.) I haven’t mentioned BTS to her at all but she must have seen my LYT poster on my wall and looked into it cus this year she gave me a BTS one hahaha

Lol, this pic is old, the boys r such babies. She’s a sweet lady though, trying to give me something I’d like even if she doesn’t understand it hehe. She may be annoying some times in the way that parents can but she’s a great mom. I thanked her and told her I was excited to see them in concert in London

summary: BTS Reactions - Their child repeats something you said during sex Your child’s brow is furrowed as he plays around with his now...
body:
BTS Reactions - Their child repeats something you said during sex

Your child’s brow is furrowed as he plays around with his now empty juice box, and you and your husband are slightly distracted. You, your husband, son and the whole of his old idol group are out for a day at the beach, and there’s so much to talk about. That’s why your son has to shout very loudly to get your husband’s attention,

“Appa! Where was eomma last night? I heard her telling you that she was coming, but wasn’t she in the bedroom the whole night?” He asks, clearly having been trying to figure out the mystery all day.

Jin

Jin smiles gently as everyone else at the table completely loses it, laughing and teasing the two of you. While you’re blushing and hiding behind your hands in shame, Jin’s taken the empty juice box and replaced it with some apple slices to distract your son just a little. They’re one of his favourite snacks (he gets too hyper on sugar, so you try to restrict it as much as is fair to him) so he’s not totally paying attention to Jin’s slightly deceptive response,

“It’s nothing you need to be worrying about, young man. I’m sure it won’t be a problem again. We should probably talk about how you were up so late, instead! I thought you were asleep after your bedtime story,” Jin teases, and you have to admit that he’s great at skirting just around these subjects. It’s not something either of you want to address until your son is much older, so it’s damn lucky that you’re married to Jin!

Yoongi

Yoongi smiles knowingly to you as he pats your thigh comfortingly. Your face is already a deep red, and all of the group is laughing to each other as they watch for your reactions. His hand squeezes your thigh one last time before turning to face his son with a fatherly smile on. It’s become one of your favourite looks for Yoongi - the adoration in his eyes, the slight curve on his lips, the way his gently ruffles his sons hair,

“Why don’t you ask eomma? She’s the one who was saying it so loudly, maybe she’ll know,” Yoongi says, pulling his son into his lap and throwing the empty juice box into the bin as he does so. Now all eyes are on you as you splutter and blush, barely able to register Yoongi’s devilish smirk as your son looks ta you expectantly.

Hoseok

Hoseok actually spits out his drink. Everyone collapses into a fit of giggles (with the exception of you and Hoseok) as his face glows red, trying to mop up the drink while trying to figure out an explanation. This is absolutely mortifying for the poor man, and now he has to lie and come up with some excuse, while everyone looks at the two of you, knowing exactly what the truth is,

“Your eo- she was- we were… well, she was fussing around in the wardrobe trying to sort out her shoes but I wanted to go to sleep,” Hoseok stutters, and you eye him carefully. He hasn’t stopped blushing, “I was telling her to hurry up, so she was letting me know that she’d come to bed in a minute,” Hoseok finishes with a sigh of relief, thinking that he’s out of the woods. Of course, with 6 close friends that overheard, that’s not going to happen anytime soon!

Namjoon

Namjoon’s eyes nearly bulge out of his head when he processes what his son just said. In all honesty, this was always going to end up happening at some point. Having children didn’t affect Namjoon’s sex drive in any manner, it’s just that the two of you have had to learn to be quieter. Clearly you’re not quite quiet enough, if your son heard enough to have to question. Luckily enough, Namjoon has been subconsciously preparing himself for this since he was born,

“It was nothing, little man. We were watching a film last night, with some people having an argument. It dis sound a little bit like your eomma though, especially since you must have been so exhausted that late,” Namjoon says with ease, handing the young boy another juice box to distract him. He even has a ready answer when his son asks if he can watch the movie too, “I don’t think so, it’s a little scary,” You chose to ignore Jungkook’s mumble of ‘I bet it is’.

Masterlist
